---
// WhatWeDoSection.astro - Core value proposition section
// Explains what Languages 4 actually does for Indigenous communities
---

<section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background decoration -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-0 w-96 h-96 bg-accent-600 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-600 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 lg:pr-24 relative z-10">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-medium text-primary-900 mb-6">
        Create a Languages 4 Project
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-neutral-700 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Unlock a world of possibilities with Languages 4â„¢: where culture, technology, and innovation converge to create an 
        <strong class="text-primary-900">immersive and accessible language learning adventure</strong>, anytime, anywhere.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three Main Pillars -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-7xl mx-auto mb-12">
      
      <!-- Pillar 1: Innovative Technology -->
      <div class="group relative bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-neutral-50 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-[0_10px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,0.08)] transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-[0_20px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)] hover:-translate-y-2">
        <!-- Icon -->
        <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6 transform transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:rotate-3 shadow-brand">
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">
          Innovative Instructional Technology
        </h3>

        <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          L4 Projects utilize innovative strategies and technologies to support language learning in the community, from Advanced Speech Recognition to Augmented Reality, to Gamification and Virtual Education.
        </p>

        <!-- Feature highlights -->
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-neutral-700">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
            </svg>
            <span>Advanced Speech Recognition for pronunciation mastery</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-neutral-700">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
