          </svg>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">
          Authentic and Rich Media
        </h3>

        <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          L4 Projects showcase the heritage language with authentic documents, thousands of animated videos, and voice recordings of speakers across the community with a range of proficiency, profile, and generation.
