        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-semibold text-primary-900 mb-4">
          When You Need It, Where You Need It
        </h3>

        <p class="text-neutral-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          L4 Projects are cloud-based, multi-platform, and ready to meet your learners at home on their computers or while playing outside on their phones or tablets!
        </p>

        <!-- Feature highlights -->
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-neutral-700">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-accent-600 mt-0.5 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
